data.description: LOCATION, QUALITY, CHARACTER!! Welcome to the Downs at Holly Creek with easy townhouse living conveniently located in the heart of Anderson. This 3 bedroom 3 bathroom, 1 owner home is IMMACULATE! When you enter, you will love the attention to detail with beautiful double crown moldings carried throughout the lower level of the home and hardwood floors carried throughout the living, kitchen, and dining area. From the entryway is Bedroom 2, a full hallway bathroom, ample hallway closet storage, and a large laundry room with a folding station with granite countertops and beautiful cabinetry. The living room is spacious and features an electric fireplace and built-in shelving and TV nook. You will LOVE the quality wooden cabinetry and granite countertops in the kitchen and owner's bathroom. The kitchen features quality stainless steel appliances, private window over the kitchen sink, pantry, and breakfast bar. The owner's suite has beautiful natural light only found in end-units, tray ceilings, walk-in closet, and a large owner's bathroom with double sinks, vanity space, walk-in shower, and jetted tub. Upstairs is an oversized 3rd bedroom that could serve as a 2nd master bedroom with a hobby room / office / flex room, full bathroom with ample storage, walk-in closet, and walk-in attic. If you enjoy the peace of the outdoors, you will love the private screened-in porch, perfect for relaxing, and the oversized patio in the private, beautifully landscaped backyard. This townhouse is in a PRIME location - 2 minutes to grocery stores, 3 minutes to the YMCA and AnMed Health Campus, 6 minutes to downtown Anderson and Anderson hospital, minutes to multiple walking trails and Lake Hartwell. This is one you must see to truly appreciate.
